/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a low angle, giving a sense of the city's towering presence. The sky above is a clear blue, providing a vibrant backdrop to the urban landscape. Trees line the sides of the street, their green foliage contrasting with the concrete structures. Buildings of various sizes and designs fill the background, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. The street itself is a hive of activity with cars and taxis in motion, adding a dynamic element to the scene. Power lines crisscross above, connecting the buildings and adding another layer of complexity to the cityscape. The image is bathed in the warm glow of the sun, which shines brightly in the top right corner, casting long shadows and highlighting the textures of the buildings and trees.
